## Section

```elixir
text = Kino.Input.textarea("Input here:")
```

## Part 1

```elixir
rations =
  text
  |> Kino.Input.read()
  |> String.split("\n\n")
  |> Enum.map(
    &(&1
      |> String.split("\n", trim: true)
      |> Enum.reduce(0, fn x, acc -> acc + String.to_integer(x) end))
  )

rations
|> Enum.sort()
|> List.last()
```

## Part 2

```elixir
rations
|> Enum.sort()
|> Enum.reverse()
|> Enum.take(3)
|> Enum.sum()
```
